reviews: Excellent fitting and nice level of tint.

review_title: Good Quality Hoop but the Spalding Rebound system won't fit.
reviews: Bought this replacement hoop along with the Spalding ball return that's supposed to fit all hoops but it doesn't because of the thicker solid steel at the back isn't drilled for it to go through.

review_title: Same great quality but fits small compared to Redmond style.
reviews: Fit on the small side but other than that looked to be the same quality as all Columbia shoes.
The material is a little heavier for quick drying but are a real nice short.

review_title: Great looking cover for the money.
reviews: Took a while to get but looks great and is a softer feel than what I expected which is great.
My son loves these shirts for golf. Wash and clean up great.
Not a very quality product. I thought Obusforme would of been a better product. Memory foam or foam flattened out in less than 2 weeks.

Ordered this hose to replace the plastic hose on my Simoniz 1800 PSI pressure washer and the housing bottoms out before the hose center seals. Going to have to find a brass washer or something to build up.
Bought it off Amazon on sale and was cheaper than ordering direct. I've always loved the Bedrug products.
The hamper collapses easily and is sturdy enough to carry full of clothes.
Look to wear well. I've been using them for laying flagstone and pavers.

review_title: DO NOT USE THESE! Order the actual REDI-SHADE Easy Lift.
reviews: It took 3 orders to get 3 blinds that could be used. Very cheap base of the blind. Also, one blind sits on an angle when i have it partially up. Make sure to get the REDI SHADE blind when ordering. Not these.
Rust showing right out of the box and pieces missing. Didn’t look too sturdy. Bought the Rhino step instead.
Will do what I want but when I contacted Curt they said the harness between the plugs had a reverse lead I could tap into but it doesn’t.
Bought this to protect my bumper and to use as a step. I also bought the front bull bar to match.
The shorter blinds I ordered in a 36” are not the same as the 48”. They do not match at all. Different material for the blinds and a different bottom. Be careful if trying to do a bay window.
I love the way these hoodies fit and feel. I am 5’9” and weigh 200 and the XL fits me great. Material doesn’t ball up as of yet and a great weight for the cold.

review_title: Great product just check for damage.
reviews: Product looks very good and sturdy. It was packaged very well except for the one container that I think was packaged broken because it was inside of another container wrapped in plastic and foam. Just a quality control problem at the packaging facility. Not going to repackage for the one container. Hopefully they stand up.
Doesn’t chop up onions very well. Leaves a lot of chunks. Not worth the money.
After the first wash/dry the length shrunk up so much I cut them off for shorts now.
Nice replacement bulb, fit fine just not as bright as I would of liked it. Using it in my painting flood lights.

review_title: Junk!! Good thing they are out of stock!
reviews: Junk! Both stopped working within a month of use.

review_title: Fit a 2019 Colorado Crew Cab Perfect!
reviews: Perfect fit as always AVS! If you follow the instructions and put the front flange behind the mirror cap you won’t have any problems. Lund International confirmed the fit on my 2019 for me. Thank you.
Very good quality paper used on this print. I wasn’t expecting that. It’s a cool piece for my son’s room.
Looks ok from a distance. Cutting of the vinyl is very jagged and was very tough to apply. Paper kept separating from the decal.
Excellent quality photo. Put it in a frame for my son and looks great!
Great quality of vinyl and easily applied even with the fine cuts.
I received this cover to use on my couch for a small dog and one cat. It is already balling up and has pulls. Everything sticks to the fabric and it is very hard to remove pet hair.
Excellent product. I’ve been wearing different arm sleeves over the last couple years and this one seems to be very high quality and fits very well with equal pressure and hasn’t stretched out yet.
This is the 3rd tv I’ve put these in and just adds the right amount of light. Remote doesn’t work too far away but may also need some quality batteries.
Looks good but looses sharpness as you move it more than 10-15’ away. I’ll have to look into the other options/designs. Emits a daylight/white light.
Works exactly as my son wanted for his gaming.
I haven’t used it yet but looks like a quality product.
Very handy for what my son has used it for so far. Great price. Haven't had a chance to use is on my Android box yet.
